(165, '_transient_dash_de3249c4736ad3bd2cd29147c4a0d43e', '<h4>Most Popular</h4>\n<h5><a href=''http://wordpress.org/plugins/better-wp-security/''>Better WP Security</a></h5>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=better-wp-security&amp;_wpnonce=2462b01f8b&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''Better WP Security''>Install</a>)</span>\n<p>The easiest, most effective way to secure WordPress. Improve the security of any WordPress site in seconds.</p>\n<h4>Newest Plugins</h4>\n<h5><a href=''http://wordpress.org/plugins/google-authenticator-per-user-prompt/''>Google Authenticator - Per User Prompt</a></h5>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=google-authenticator-per-user-prompt&amp;_wpnonce=b1dadd7e81&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''Google Authenticator - Per User Prompt''>Install</a>)</span>\n<p>Modifies the Google Authenticator plugin so that only users with 2FA enabled are prompted for the authentication token.</p>\n', 'no'),
