gin.com/?p=8768";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:587:"<p>Today a small, but big, issue came to light with the AdRotate blocks. Small because it was only 1 pixel being wrong. But big because a whole bunch of blocks broke because of it. This has been tested and a patch has been verified on several servers. This update fixes the issue. Changes (Pro and [&#8230;]</p><p>The post <a href="http://www.adrotateplugin.com/2013/11/adrotate-pro-3-8-15-adrotate-free-3-8-11-fixing-blocks/">AdRotate Pro 3.8.15 and AdRotate Free 3.8.11 &#8211; Fixing blocks</a> appeared first on <a href="http://www.adrotateplugin.com">AdRotate for WordPress</a>.</p>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:13:"Arnan de Gans";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:837:"<p>Today a small, but big, issue came to light with the AdRotate blocks. Small because it was only 1 pixel being wrong. But big because a whole bunch of blocks broke because of it.<br />\nThis has been tested and a patch has been verified on several servers.</p>\n<p>This update fixes the issue.</p>\n<h3>Changes (Pro and Free versions)</h3>\n<div class="shortcode-unorderedlist arrow"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>[fix] Block size calculated properly</li>\n</ul>\n<p></div>\n\n<p>The post <a href="http://www.adrotateplugin.com/2013/11/adrotate-pro-3-8-15-adrotate-free-3-8-11-fixing-blocks/">AdRotate Pro 3.8.15 and AdRotate Free 3.8.11 &#8211; Fixing blocks</a> appeared first on <a href="http://www.adrotateplugin.com">AdRotate for WordPress</a>.</p><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/AdrotatePluginForWordpress/~4/skexlC6TuQE" height="1" width="1"/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:98:"http://www.adrotateplugin.com/2013/11/adrotate-pro-3-8-15-adrotate-free-3-8-11-fixing-blocks/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:42:"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0";a:1:{s:8:"origLink";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:93:"http://www.adrotateplugin.com/2013/11/adrotate-pro-3-8-15-adrotate-free-3-8-11-fixing-blocks/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:57:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:6:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:38:"Bugs in blocks and broken credit cards";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:73:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/AdrotatePluginForWordpress/~3/i8vsT6EohbA/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:79:"http://www.adrotateplugin.com/2013/11/bugs-blocks-broken-credit-cards/#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Tue, 26 Nov 2013 19:03:47 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:4:"News";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{